Salado first appeared as a [[census designated place]] in the [[1980 United States census]].<ref name=1980CensusTX/> After incorporation, it was listed as a village in the [[2010 U.S. census]].<ref name=2010CensusTX/> It is part of the [[Killeen, Texas|Killeen]]&ndash;[[Temple, Texas|Temple]]&ndash;[[Fort Hood]] [[Killeen-Temple-Fort Hood metropolitan area|Metropolitan Statistical Area]].

